# fastapi

> AGENTS.md: instructions for AI coding agents working on this project.
> Human contributors: see README.md.

## Stack

- Python
- FastAPI

## Commands

(no commands detected. Fill in the commands agents should run for build, test, lint, etc.)

## Conventions

- Type hints on every public function. Run mypy or pyright in CI.
- Format with black or ruff-format. Lint with ruff.
- Group routes into `APIRouter`s by resource. Mount them from `main.py`.
- Pydantic models for request and response shapes. Annotate return types for OpenAPI.
- `async def` endpoints. Move CPU work to `run_in_threadpool` so the event loop stays free.
- Poetry-managed: `poetry install`, `poetry run uvicorn <app>:app --reload`. Deps live in pyproject.toml.

## What to avoid

- Bare `except:` clauses. Catch the specific exception.
- Blocking calls (sync DB drivers, `time.sleep`) in `async` endpoints.

